Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.08,0:00:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右臂被帶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.44,0:00:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交喙 小鷺 鳶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.27,0:00:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鷺 情況報告
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.53,0:00:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕雀和鴉稍微偏離了跳躍的座標
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.18,0:00:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梟無法確認
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.69,0:00:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 紅秧 你的手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.50,0:00:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的手沒關係 看樣子是丟失了電子終端
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.33,0:00:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳶 就停在這個時空間
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.94,0:00:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.47,0:00:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時空正在動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.74,0:02:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(460,320)\fad(300,0)\bord0\be1\1c&Hdca561&}離\N  \N家\N  \N出\N  \N走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.24,0:02:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對你來說 你是做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.29,0:02:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是救不了這個少女的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.79,0:02:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.36,0:02:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.85,0:02:50.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要管他
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.08,0:02:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我知道你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.02,0:03:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 你的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.77,0:03:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 龍之轉矩原來是人類啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.57,0:03:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燕雀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我先找到的 鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍之轉矩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.34,0:03:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍之轉矩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.12,0:03:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙就由我來運走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.83,0:03:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 燕雀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.77,0:03:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍之轉矩有可能承受不了轉移的衝擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.86,0:03:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是一隻手臂也好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.33,0:03:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙的量子碎片 帶回去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:11.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想一個人獨佔功勞嗎 鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:15.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在和紅秧取得聯絡以前 避免擅自行動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.21,0:04:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熵增值情況惡化
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.21,0:04:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}注釋：在封閉的熱力體系中不能做功的一定數量的熱能的計量單位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:40.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時空開始動搖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.32,0:04:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.08,0:04:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為是量子自旋覺醒反應的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.54,0:04:49.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個時空使用了量子自旋壁嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.85,0:04:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去的話將造成內部資料的侵犯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.35,0:04:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間的流逝開始減速了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.94,0:05:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.33,0:05:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間 停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.38,0:05:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要打了 時空發生了共鳴現象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.04,0:05:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 鴉 我討厭你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.45,0:05:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道嗎 就算你現在消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.32,0:05:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只會當作是在作戰中被彈到時空的哪個角落裏去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.80,0:05:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰也不會覺得不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.96,0:05:44.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.87,0:05:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.32,0:06:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.13,0:06:18.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我不會手下留情了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.09,0:06:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是兩個人打鬥的時候嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:38.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梟 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.64,0:06:40.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉移座標有了誤差
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.24,0:06:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 找到了沒有 龍之轉矩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.56,0:06:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是 龍之轉矩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不能安定下來 要解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.04,0:07:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退 同僚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.65,0:07:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.95,0:07:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遙 那些傢伙呢 那些傢伙到哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.92,0:07:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.41,0:07:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 遙 在哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.89,0:07:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 沒有被怎麼樣吧 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:49.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈呢 看到靈界的入口了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.46,0:07:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美保 你閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.81,0:07:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你不要打岔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那是幽靈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.54,0:07:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.42,0:08:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 發生什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.70,0:08:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.14,0:08:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事也沒有 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.89,0:08:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機艦 好像完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.41,0:08:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅秧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.92,0:08:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅秧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.86,0:08:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輸入測試發送
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行資料處理
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.84,0:09:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳥兒們的時空轉移好像不怎麼穩定啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.06,0:09:18.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功率上升了 不需要擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.76,0:09:21.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 鳥兒們只剩下七隻了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.36,0:09:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要剩下一隻 就可能奪回龍之轉矩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:30.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 監視的鳥兒還存在著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.97,0:09:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼龍之轉矩存在的時空是不會扭曲的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.76,0:09:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,存在已經確認了 不會錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.12,0:09:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要把龍之轉矩得到手 就可以阻止香格里拉的侵入
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的能奪回龍之轉矩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.65,0:09:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敗的話 我們所存在的這個拉庫利瑪時空界將被消滅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.04,0:10:08.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時空 是時間15年前的時間點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.95,0:10:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且是相近的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.03,0:10:15.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我們的過去無限接近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 我 還有那傢伙也存在的時空
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.59,0:10:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是諷刺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.73,0:10:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們完成被交付的任務就好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.40,0:10:38.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照離子的秩序讓時空安定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.05,0:10:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我們龍騎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住嘴 鴉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:46.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經不再被任何東西支配
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,責任 需求 都不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.28,0:10:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:11:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我大概是從以前開始就只是希望再看到夢想一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.95,0:11:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.29,0:11:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是變的很奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.71,0:11:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不是夢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.15,0:11:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.38,0:11:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.55,0:12:03.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊 遙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.63,0:12:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 會來不及
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.66,0:12:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊 是你睡過頭了不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.62,0:12:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 就是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.66,0:12:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了就停下來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.55,0:12:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.24,0:12:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 好像狗一樣 跑的太快啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是狗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.83,0:12:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.67,0:12:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧 愛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.17,0:12:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.46,0:12:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.39,0:12:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不要把我的車劃傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.96,0:12:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪惠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.13,0:12:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 頂上凹下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:45.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.14,0:12:53.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能 不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.31,0:12:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪惠 你是不相信我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.41,0:12:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有那回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.74,0:12:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要一邊吃東西一邊說話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.10,0:13:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那絕對是真的 終於見到了 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.33,0:13:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 藤原還被抓住腳發出絲絲的聲音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.63,0:13:10.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.50,0:13:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不要那樣做了 那麼晚只有你們幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.72,0:13:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是沒事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.41,0:13:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是 我跑的很快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.09,0:13:20.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是說那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.21,0:13:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 我也聽說了那個傳聞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.66,0:13:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.06,0:13:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 雪慧 告訴我 告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.81,0:13:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我媽從附近的阿姨那裏聽到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.11,0:13:38.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了啊 在8號坡道 出現了只有手的幽靈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有手？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我們見到的傢伙很相似啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.71,0:13:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太厲害了 街上充滿了幽靈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.36,0:13:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太厲害了啊 那麼說 說不定會有再見到的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.75,0:13:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是緊張啊 興奮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.46,0:14:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要好好的去私塾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.98,0:14:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.63,0:14:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的話一定能合格的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.54,0:14:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有關係的 你一定能到東京的...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我才不想參加考試呢 也不想去東京
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.55,0:14:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的將來我要自己決定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.24,0:14:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊 你還辦不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.86,0:14:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是辦不到的 辦不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.28,0:14:37.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 你是媽媽最寶...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.08,0:14:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.25,0:15:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.63,0:15:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.69,0:15:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下啊 喲 什麼啊 那個裝扮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.41,0:15:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備離家出走嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.47,0:15:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能嘛 你是個努力學習的人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.35,0:15:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 還真是多才呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.65,0:15:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把寫了必勝的頭帶綁在頭上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要學習 要合格
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.63,0:15:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學習 合格 學習 合格
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.77,0:15:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.43,0:15:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私塾什麼的不要去上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.59,0:15:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去你要垮了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.06,0:15:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一起踢足球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.53,0:15:59.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年為止還是部員的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.27,0:16:05.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有像勇那樣的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:14.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要考慮狀態 玩的高興就好 玩的高興
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.31,0:16:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正勇是不明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.60,0:16:19.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.99,0:16:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.99,0:16:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽的祈禱嗎 裝什麼好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.36,0:16:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 我不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.77,0:16:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡不對了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.11,0:16:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇是不明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.00,0:16:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤原
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.81,0:16:33.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.10,0:16:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.29,0:16:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.54,0:16:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 你們在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.07,0:16:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 藤原
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 你們看著辦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.43,0:16:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤原
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.22,0:16:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.28,0:17:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個旅行包 準備離家出走嗎 佑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要跟過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說了要離家出走就一起走的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.31,0:17:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是不準備離家出走嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔可能是沒一起住 可是阿姨相信你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叔叔也是 一定很想念你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.81,0:17:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家不一樣 支離破碎的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.20,0:17:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我 嘴上說擔心的 其實完全不是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.00,0:17:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有那樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.97,0:17:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少胡說了 明明知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.30,0:17:41.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.19,0:17:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是約定好了嗎 一起離家出走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.80,0:17:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去佑想去的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.16,0:18:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 幹什麼到這裏來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.88,0:18:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果要離家出走 暫時不會回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.98,0:18:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以最後看一下街道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.11,0:18:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心一點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.56,0:18:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 這裏 這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.07,0:18:35.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.15,0:18:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.17,0:18:39.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.87,0:18:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好高哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.98,0:18:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.61,0:18:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 車子就像米粒一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.37,0:18:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽也想看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.47,0:18:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.42,0:18:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一次看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.47,0:19:30.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.95,0:19:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.58,0:19:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就睡在這裏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.30,0:19:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.12,0:19:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又沒關係 反正離家出走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.56,0:19:40.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.90,0:19:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 好像累了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.33,0:19:45.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個借我了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.60,0:19:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.53,0:19:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的事情 不是夢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.14,0:20:03.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也看見了吧 那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.40,0:20:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的才不是幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.87,0:20:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.47,0:20:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.13,0:20:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙把我當作傻瓜了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.88,0:20:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說我什麼也做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.34,0:20:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是辦不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.12,0:20:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辦不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:26.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.18,0:20:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.16,0:20:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽見什麼聲音了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.38,0:20:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.78,0:20:49.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.83,0:20:50.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有誰在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.42,0:20:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.69,0:20:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.56,0:21:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.32,0:21:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑也看的見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.26,0:21:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 看的見 有人在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.52,0:21:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:23.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個孩子 之前來這裏看到過的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.19,0:21:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 這裏 這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.35,0:21:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙...騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.03,0:21:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在看傍晚的海市蜃樓麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是海市蜃樓 也不是幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.44,0:21:43.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是時空的凝聚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.72,0:21:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.42,0:21:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是海市蜃樓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.06,0:21:49.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也並非幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.74,0:21:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.22,0:21:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 遙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.85,0:21:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始直到結束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.89,0:21:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後再一次開始重複
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.11,0:22:01.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了存在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.21,0:22:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不斷周而復始...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.75,0:22:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 聽不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.78,0:22:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.90,0:22:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳶 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.84,0:22:39.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,座標又偏移了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.66,0:23:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟著呢 我離那個傢伙最近
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.78,0:23:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍之轉矩 由我...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.52,0:24:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在做夢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.47,0:24:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個夏天的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.65,0:24:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.04,0:24:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.93,0:25:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.59,0:25:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 結束後...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.99,0:25:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰來救救我
